    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about the money though. it's like, i look at them and i realize that every day i'm here, i'm just consuming resources. food, electricity, space... i'm just a drain on everything they have. if i wasn't here, she wouldn't have to worry about my debt or my moods or how much i'm failing them. it feels like the math just doesn't add up in my favor anymore. i'm just a net negative in their lives.",
